import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import CoverVideoScript from '../CoverVideoScript/CoverVideoScript'
import LottieScript from '../lottieScript/LottieScript'

const VideoContainer = styled.div`
width: 100%;
`
const CoverVideo = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <script src="../lottieScript/LottieScript.js"></script>
    <VideoContainer id="lottie">
    </VideoContainer>
    <script src="../CoverVideoScript/CoverVideoScript.js"></script>
    </>
  )
}

export default CoverVideo
